  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/9a19a5b35959b45e8931812cfd31be2c.poster.avif?t=1729863286\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/9a19a5b35959b45e8931812cfd31be2c.webm?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/9a19a5b35959b45e8931812cfd31be2c.mp4?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>The legendary O-Core, once humanity’s main AI, has rebelled and now rules an expanding robotic empire, called Ostallians and launching attacks on Earth and countless worlds. <br>Destroy the Core’s heavily-defended server installations and halt its conquest!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Core Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 80's and 90's ASCII atmosphere meets modern effects in a story-driven Space Opera<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/1572928e79ab2886103b31f71db59cd3.poster.avif?t=1729863286\" width=630 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/1572928e79ab2886103b31f71db59cd3.webm?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/1572928e79ab2886103b31f71db59cd3.mp4?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> A highly engaging feature where bases connected in a chain are destroyed in sequence<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/d85f981595618a3446beb8a2454d018f.poster.avif?t=1729863286\" width=630 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/d85f981595618a3446beb8a2454d018f.webm?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/d85f981595618a3446beb8a2454d018f.mp4?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Play with diverse spaceships and explore different space worlds and their sublevels, each with its own unique environment<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/f978b5eef20ed318d17ec6d2bcb1ee05.poster.avif?t=1729863286\" width=630 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/f978b5eef20ed318d17ec6d2bcb1ee05.webm?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/f978b5eef20ed318d17ec6d2bcb1ee05.mp4?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Customize your ship and upgrade it with some RPG elements <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/2c89c784ca231dab9d4523111719250f.poster.avif?t=1729863286\" width=630 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/2c89c784ca231dab9d4523111719250f.webm?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/2c89c784ca231dab9d4523111719250f.mp4?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Unleash a variety of Power-Ups during intense gameplay sessions<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/d7d024bcd2c97d7dfe39f02afce4f036.poster.avif?t=1729863286\" width=630 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/d7d024bcd2c97d7dfe39f02afce4f036.webm?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/d7d024bcd2c97d7dfe39f02afce4f036.mp4?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Encounter special boss events<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/965bf8ab3c5b90a76e9644da42af7067.poster.avif?t=1729863286\" width=630 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/965bf8ab3c5b90a76e9644da42af7067.webm?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/965bf8ab3c5b90a76e9644da42af7067.mp4?t=1729863286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Replay the sessions with various difficulty levels you will unlock after completing the game<br><br></li><li> Compete for the highest score and dominate the leaderboard</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887880/extras/5080600b12ea2184bbfc2b430cf6b1b4.avif?t=1729863286\" width=650 height=366 /></span>",
